                <h1>How to Update Your Public Profile on Snapchat</h1>
                <p>To edit your public profile on Snapchat, open the app and tap on your Bitmoji. Select 'View My Profile,' then click 'Edit Profile.' Here, you can update your profile picture, add a bio, and choose visibility settings. Don't forget to save your changes before exiting the menu to ensure your updates are applied!</p>
